description: This Chainlink VRF top 9% rating Gatinho purrs with a rating of 74, and a multiplier of 1x. It has a total score of 74, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Nine Lives for North, Nine Lives for East, 1 for South, and Stringalong for West. Gatinho has the personality suit of punter. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/50741-99172-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Gatinho [74 Votes, Top 9% Rating]
